lemma succswitch: 
  assumes "∀s. ∃succ. s ∈ S' ⟶ P s succ"
  shows "∃succ. ∀s ∈ S'. P s (succ s)" 
  using assms by metis

subsection ‹Proposition 40›

lemma proposition40:
  assumes "¬dependvar f M 0"
  and "¬dependvar g M 0"
  and "finite A"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦μ g ∧⇩μ (f ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts A⟩⇩R var 0)⟧ M e =
  (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e)"
  (is "s ∈ ⟦μ ?f⟧ M e = ?R s")   
proof
  let ?S' = "{s. ∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e}"
  have "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∩ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ⟹ validfinpath M s [] s ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin []) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin []) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" by simp
  hence "⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∩ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ⊆ ?S'" by blast
  moreover {
    fix s
    assume "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∩ ⟦⟨Acts A⟩⇩R var 0⟧ M (newenvironment e ?S')"
    then obtain act s' p s'' where "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∧ act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" by (auto simp: assms)
    hence "validfinpath M s ((s, act, s')#p) s'' ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin ((s, act, s')#p)) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin ((s, act, s')#p)) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" by auto
    hence "s ∈  ?S'" by blast
  }
  ultimately have "⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∩ (⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ ⟦⟨Acts A⟩⇩R var 0⟧ M (newenvironment e ?S')) ⊆ ?S'" by blast
  hence "⟦g⟧ M (newenvironment e ?S') ∩ (⟦f⟧ M (newenvironment e ?S') ∪ ⟦⟨Acts A⟩⇩R var 0⟧ M (newenvironment e ?S')) ⊆ ?S'" by (simp add: assms notdependshiftdown) 
  moreover assume "s ∈ ⟦mu ?f⟧ M e"
  ultimately show "?R s" by auto 
next
  assume assum1: "?R s"
  then obtain p s' where assum1: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" by auto
  show "s ∈ ⟦mu ?f⟧ M e"
    apply (simp add: assms notdependshiftdown del: occurssimps)
    apply (rule allI)
  proof
    fix X
    assume inX : "⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ∩ (⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ X}) ⊆ X"
    have "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ⟶
          alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X"
      apply (induct p arbitrary: s; rule impI)
      apply simp
      using inX apply blast
    proof-
      fix t p s
      assume IH: "⋀s. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e ⟶ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X"
      assume assum1: "validfinpath M s (t # p) s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin (t # p)) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (t # p)) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e"
      hence "validfinpath M (target t) p s' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ alloccurringstates (target t) (fin p) ⊆ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" by simp
      hence alloccurringtail: "alloccurringstates (target t) (fin p) ⊆ X" using IH by blast
      hence "target t ∈ X ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ (source t, action t, target t) ∈ transition M ∧ source t ∈ ⟦shiftdown g 0⟧ M e" using assum1 by auto
      hence "source t ∈ X" using inX by blast
      thus "alloccurringstates s (fin (t # p)) ⊆ X" using alloccurringtail assum1 by simp
    qed
    thus "s ∈ X" using assum1 by simp
  qed
qed

subsection ‹Theorem 21›

lemma invariantApath : 
  assumes "S' ⊆ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' a. a ∈ A ∧ (s, a, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'}"
  and "s ∈ S' ∩ {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e }"
  shows "∃s' a. a ∈ A ∧ (s, a, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S' ∩ {s'. ∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e}"
proof-
  have "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s' a. a ∈ A ∧ (s, a, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S')" using assms by auto
  moreover have "s ∉ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e"
    apply (rule ccontr, simp)
  proof-
    assume "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e" 
    hence "validfinpath M s [] s ∧ alloccurringactions (fin []) ⊆ A ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e" by auto
    thus False using assms(2) by blast
  qed
  ultimately obtain a s' where assum1 : "a ∈ A ∧ (s, a, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'" by auto  
  have "∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e"
    apply (rule ccontr, simp)
  proof-
    assume "∃p. action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ (∃s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e)"
    then obtain p s'' where "validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e " by auto
    hence "validfinpath M s ((s, a, s')#p) s'' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin ((s, a, s')#p)) ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e " using assum1 by simp
    thus False using assms(2) by blast
  qed
  thus ?thesis using assum1 by auto
qed

lemma theorem21generalized :  
  assumes "¬dependvar f M 0"
  and "finite A"
  shows "(s ∈ ⟦ν f ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts A⟩⇩R var 0⟧ M e) =
  ((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e) ∨ 
  (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ alloccurringactions (inf p) ⊆ A))"
  (is "s ∈ ⟦ν ?f⟧ M e = (?R⇩1 s ∨ ?R⇩2 s)")
  apply (rule iffI)
  defer
  apply (simp add: assms(2) del: Diamond.simps)
  apply (subst notdependshiftdown)
  apply (simp add: assms(1))
  apply (rule exI)
proof
  assume "s ∈ ⟦nu ?f⟧ M e"
  hence "∃S'. S' ⊆ ⟦f⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'} ∧ s ∈ S'" using assms(2) by (simp del: Diamond.simps)
  then obtain S' where "S' ⊆ ⟦f⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'} ∧ s ∈ S'" by auto
  hence assum1 : "S' ⊆ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'} ∧ s ∈ S'" using assms(1) notdependshiftdown by blast
  have "¬?R⇩1 s ⟹ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ (∀n. action (p n) ∈ A))"
    apply (rule successorlemma)
  proof-
    assume assum2 : "¬?R⇩1 s"
    let ?S' = "S' ∩ {s'. ¬?R⇩1 s'}" 
    have "(∀s'. (s' ∈ ?S' ⟶ (∃t. source t = s' ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ target t ∈ ?S')))"
      apply (rule allI)
    proof
      fix s
      assume assum3 : "s ∈ ?S'"
      have "S' ⊆ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S'} ⟹ s ∈ S' ∩ {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ set (map action p) ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e } ⟹ ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ S' ∩ {s'. ∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e}" using invariantApath by simp
      hence "∃s'' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s'') ∈ (transition M) ∧ s'' ∈ ?S'" using assum1 assum3 assms(1) by simp
      thus "∃t. source t = s ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ target t ∈ ?S'" by auto
    qed
    moreover have "s ∈ ?S'" using assum1 assum2 by auto
    ultimately show "s ∈ ?S' ∧ (∀s'. (s' ∈ ?S' ⟶ (∃t. source t = s' ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ target t ∈ ?S')))" by simp
  qed
  thus "?R⇩1 s ∨ ?R⇩2 s" by (simp only: image_subset_iff alloccurringmap.simps; auto)
next
  let ?S' = "{s. ?R⇩1 s ∨ ?R⇩2 s}"
  assume "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ action ` range p ⊆ A)"
  thus "s ∈ ?S'" by simp
  show "?S' ⊆ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ ?S'}"
  proof
    fix s
    assume "s ∈ ?S'"
    moreover {  
      assume "?R⇩1 s"
      then obtain p s' where assum1 : "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e" by auto
      have "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ (∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e))"
        apply (induct p arbitrary : s; simp)
      proof-
        fix t p
        assume "t ∈ transition M ∧ validfinpath M (target t) p s' ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e"
        hence "(source t, action t, target t) ∈ transition M ∧ (validfinpath M (target t) p s' ∧ action t ∈ A ∧ action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e)" using splittransition by metis
        thus "source t ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (source t, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ (∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ action ` set p ⊆ A ∧ s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e))" by blast
      qed
      hence "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ ?S'}" using assum1 by auto
    }
    moreover {
      assume "?R⇩2 s"
      then obtain p where assum1 :"validinfpath M s p ∧ (∀n. action (p n) ∈ A)" unfolding alloccurringmap.simps by blast
      hence "s = source (p 0) ∧ (p 0) ∈ transition M ∧ action (p 0) ∈ A ∧ validinfpath M (target (p 0)) (suffix (Suc 0) p) ∧ (∀n. action ((suffix (Suc 0) p) n) ∈ A)" by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
      hence "(s, action (p 0), target (p 0)) ∈ transition M  ∧ action (p 0) ∈ A ∧ validinfpath M (target (p 0)) (suffix (Suc 0) p) ∧ (∀n. action ((suffix (Suc 0) p) n) ∈ A)" by simp
      hence "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ ?S'}" unfolding alloccurringmap.simps using assum1 by blast
   }
   ultimately show "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown f 0⟧ M e ∪ {s. ∃s' act. act ∈ A ∧ (s, act, s') ∈ transition M ∧ s' ∈ ?S'}" by blast
 qed
qed

theorem theorem21 :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ [Acts (-B)]⇩R ff ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)⟧ M e 
    = (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ progressing M B s p)"
  apply (subst negformula)
proof-
  have "∀s. s ∈ ⟦Diamond ρ (nu (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (Box (Acts (-B)) ff)) (Diamond (Acts (-α⇩f)) (var 0))))⟧ M e 
    = (∃p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ progressing M B s p )"
    apply (subst Diamondmatch)
    apply (simp add: assms splitviolating del: formulasemantics.simps)
    apply (subst theorem21generalized; ((subst alloccursnotoccurs)+)?; simp add: assms notoccursnotdepends Boxcomplement_locked Diamond_enabled del: Diamond.simps Box.simps Diamond_eq_exist Box_eq_forall occurssimps)
  proof
    have "⋀s'. (∃p. validpath M s' p ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p α⇩f α⇩e ∧ progressing M B s' p) = ((∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p))) "
      by (subst freeuntiloccurrenceprogressing_lockedenabled; simp)
    thus "⋀s. (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ ((∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s'' α⇩e ∨ locked M B s'')) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p)))) = (∃p p' s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ validpath M s' p' ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p' α⇩f α⇩e ∧ progressing M B s' p')" by blast
  qed
  thus "(s ∉ ⟦Diamond ρ (nu (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (Box (Acts (-B)) ff)) (Diamond (Acts (-α⇩f)) (var 0))))⟧ M e) = (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ progressing M B s p)" by blast
qed

subsection ‹Lemma 50›

lemma lemma50 : 
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (α⇩_el a)"
  and "¬dependvar (φ_off a) M 0"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (φ_off a ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (α⇩_el a -α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)⟧ M (newenvironment e S') 
    = (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ 
        (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off a) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ ((α⇩_el a) - α⇩f) ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))"
  apply (subst Diamondmatch)
  apply (simp add: assms enabled_def)
  apply (subst matchstaract)
  apply (simp add: assms)
  apply (subst alloccursnotoccurs; subst notdependshiftdown; simp add: assms)
  apply meson
  done 

subsection ‹Theorem 24›
                                 
lemma occursactionorstate : 
  assumes "⋀s'. (∃p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ locked M B s'') ⟹ s' ∈ S'"
  and "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s' ∧ (occurs A (fin p) ∨ occursstate S'' s (fin p))"
  shows "∃p' s'. validfinpath M s p' s' ∧ ((s' ∈ S' ∩ S'') ∨ (∃a s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ a ∈ A ∧ s'' ∈ S'))"
proof-
  have "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s' ⟹ (∀i < length p. source (p!i) ∈ S')"
    apply (rule allI)
  proof
    fix i
    assume assum1 : "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'"
    assume "i < length p"
    hence "validfinpath M (source (p!i)) (drop i p) s' ∧ locked M B s'" using assum1 by auto
    moreover have "¬occurs α⇩f (fin (drop i p))" using assum1 by (subst notoccursfinright; blast)
    ultimately show "source (p!i) ∈ S'" using assms by blast
  qed
  hence "∀i < length p. source (p!i) ∈ S'" using assms by auto
  hence "set (map source p) ⊆ S'" using occurs_map_exists_fin subsetI by metis
  moreover have "s' ∈ S'"
  proof-
    have "validfinpath M s' [] s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin []) ∧ locked M B s'" using assms by auto
    thus "s' ∈ S'" using assms by metis
  qed
  ultimately have "insert s' (set (map source p)) ⊆ S'" by simp
  moreover have "(insert s' (set (map source p)) ⊆ S') = (insert s (set (map target p)) ⊆ S')" by (subst sourcetargetfin[of M _ _ s']; simp add: assms)
  ultimately have allstatesinS' : "s ∈ S' ∧ (∀i< length p. target (p!i) ∈ S')" by (simp add: subset_iff)
  {
    assume "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ occurs A (fin p)"
    moreover from this obtain i where "i < length p ∧ action (p!i) ∈ A" using occursfinalternative by blast
    ultimately have "validfinpath M s (take i p) (source (p!i)) ∧ (source (p!i), action (p!i), target (p!i)) ∈ transition M ∧ action (p!i) ∈ A ∧ target (p!i) ∈ S'" using allstatesinS' by auto
    hence "∃p' s'. validfinpath M s p' s' ∧ (∃a s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ a ∈ A ∧ s'' ∈ S')" by blast
  }
  moreover {
    assume assum1: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ occursstate S'' s (fin p)"
    hence "s ∈ S'' ∨ (∃i < length p. target (p!i) ∈ S'')" unfolding occursstatealternative by auto
    moreover have "s ∈ S'' ⟹ validfinpath M s [] s ∧ s ∈ S' ∩ S''"using assum1 allstatesinS' by auto
    moreover {
      assume "∃i < length p. target (p!i) ∈ S''" 
      then obtain i where assum2 : "i < length p ∧ target (p!i) ∈ S''" by auto
      hence "validfinpath M s (take i p) (source (p!i)) ∧ (source (p!i), action (p!i), target (p!i)) ∈ transition M" using assum1 by auto
      hence "validfinpath M s ((take i p) @ [(source (p!i), action (p!i), target (p!i))]) (target (p!i)) ∧ (target (p!i)) ∈ S''" using assum2 by simp
      hence "∃p' s'. validfinpath M s p' s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∩ S''" using assum2 allstatesinS' by blast
    }
    ultimately have "∃p' s'. validfinpath M s p' s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∩ S''" by blast
  }
  ultimately show ?thesis using assms by blast
qed

lemma feasiblesublemma :
  assumes exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e "
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  and reachable: "⋀s T. s ∈ S' ∧ T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)))"
  and "finite 𝒯"
  and "∃T ∈ 𝒯. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  shows "s ∈ S' ⟹ ∃p s'. p ≠ [] ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p))"
proof-
  assume assum1: "s ∈ S'"
  have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p))"
    apply (induct 𝒯 rule: inductfiniteset)
    apply (simp add: assms)
    apply (subgoal_tac "validfinpath M s [] s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin [])")
    using assum1 apply blast
    apply simp
  proof-
    fix T A'
    case (3 T A')
    then obtain p s' where IH : "T ∈ 𝒯 - A' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p))" by auto
    have "(s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ∨ (s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p))" by auto
    moreover {
      assume "s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p)"
      hence "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T'. T' ∈ insert T A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T') 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T') 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T') (fin p))" using IH by blast
    }
    moreover {
      assume "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)"
      moreover have "T ∈ 𝒯" using IH by auto
      ultimately obtain p' s'' where validpath: "validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ s'' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ ((occurs (α_el T) (fin p') ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s' (fin p')))" using IH persistent reachable by metis
      hence "(occurs (α_el T) (extendfinpath p (fin p')) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (extendfinpath p (fin p')))" using occursleftorright IH validfinpathlaststate by metis
      moreover have "∀T'. T' ∈ A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T') 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T') 0⟧ M e) s (extendfinpath p (fin p')) ∨ occurs (α_el T') (extendfinpath p (fin p'))" using IH occursleftorright by metis
      ultimately have "validfinpath M s (p @ p') s'' ∧ s'' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p @ p')) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin (p @ p')) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin (p @ p'))) ∧
        (∀T'. T' ∈ A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T') 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T') 0⟧ M e) s (fin (p @ p')) ∨ occurs (α_el T') (fin (p @ p')))" using validpath IH by auto
      hence "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T'. T' ∈ insert T A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T') 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T') 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T') (fin p))" by blast
    }
    ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T'. T' ∈ insert T A' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T') 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T') 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T') (fin p))" by blast
  qed
  moreover have "⋀p. (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ p ≠ []" using assms(5) exclusive by auto
  ultimately show ?thesis by auto
qed

lemma constructfairpath :
  assumes exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e "
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  and reachable: "∀s ∈ S'. ∀T ∈ 𝒯. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)))"
  and "finite 𝒯"
  and "⋀s. s ∈ S' ⟹ ∃T ∈ 𝒯. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  shows "s ∈ S' ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p))))))"
proof-
  assume assum1: "s ∈ S'"
  have "∀s ∈ S'. ∃p. p ≠ [] ∧ validfinpath M s p (laststate_nonexhaustive p) ∧ laststate_nonexhaustive p ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p))" 
  (is "∀s ∈ S'. ?P s")
  proof
    fix s
    assume "s ∈ S'"
    hence "∃p s'. p ≠ [] ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin p))" 
      apply (subst feasiblesublemma)
      using exclusive persistent reachable assms(4) assms(5) apply blast+
      done
    thus "?P s" using validfinpathlaststate laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive by metis
  qed
  then obtain succ where assum2: "∀s' ∈ S'. succ s' ≠ [] ∧ validfinpath M s' (succ s') (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')) ∧ laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s') ∈ S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (succ s')) ∧ (∀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s' (fin (succ s')) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin (succ s')))" by metis
  let ?p = "recursiveconcpaths succ s"
  have validinfpath: "validinfpath M s ?p" using validinfpathconc assum1 assum2 by metis
  moreover have "¬occurs α⇩f (inf ?p)"
    apply (subst occursinfalternative) 
    apply (subst validpredconc [of "λs. λp. ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p)" _ "λs. λt. action (t) ∉ α⇩f"])
    using assum1 assum2 apply auto
    done
  moreover have "∀a ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (?p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on a) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el a) (inf (suffix i ?p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off a) 0⟧ M e) (source (?p i)) (inf (suffix i ?p)))))"
    apply (rule ballI allI)+
  proof
    fix T i
    assume Tintasks: "T ∈ 𝒯"
    assume phion: "source (?p i) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
    obtain j s' where assum3: "s' ∈ S' ∧ j < length (succ s') ∧ suffix i ?p = conc (drop j (succ s')) (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')))" using suffix_recursiveconcpaths assum1 assum2 by metis
    moreover have "validinfpath M (source (?p i)) (suffix i ?p)" using validinfpath validinfsubpathright by metis
    moreover have laststate: "drop j (succ s') ≠ [] ∧ laststate (source (?p i)) (drop j (succ s')) = laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')" using assum3 by (simp add: laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive)
    ultimately have "validfinpath M (source (?p i)) (drop j (succ s')) (laststate (source (?p i)) (drop j (succ s')))" using validinfpathsplitlaststate by metis
    { 
      moreover assume "¬occurs (α_el T) (fin (drop j (succ s'))) ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (?p i)) (fin (drop j (succ s')))"
      ultimately have "laststate (source (?p i)) (drop j (succ s')) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e" using persistent Tintasks phion by metis
      hence "occurs (α_el T) (fin (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')))) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (laststate (source (?p i)) (drop j (succ s'))) (fin (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s'))))" using Tintasks assum2 assum3 laststate by metis
    } 
    hence "occurs (α_el T) (extendfinpath (drop j (succ s')) (fin (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s'))))) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (?p i)) (extendfinpath (drop j (succ s')) (fin (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')))))" using occursleftorright by metis
    hence res1: "occurs (α_el T) (fin (drop j (succ s') @ (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s'))))) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (?p i)) (fin (drop j (succ s') @ (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')))))" by simp
    have "inf (suffix i ?p) = extendfinpath (drop j (succ s')) (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s'))))" using assum3 by auto
    moreover have "succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')) ≠ []" using assum2 assum3 by auto    
    ultimately have "inf (suffix i ?p) = extendfinpath ((drop j (succ s')) @ (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')))) (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ (laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s'))))))" by (simp add: unfoldrecursiveconcpaths)
    thus "occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i ?p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (?p i)) (inf (suffix i ?p))"  using occursleft occursstateleft res1 by metis
  qed
  ultimately show ?thesis by blast
qed

lemma infpathoccursoroccursstate : 
  assumes "validinfpath M s p ∧ (occurs A (inf p) ∨ occursstate S' s (inf p))"
  shows "∃i. source (p i) ∈ S' ∨ action (p i) ∈ A" 
  using assms ind.simps(2) occursinfalternative occursstatealternative validinfpath_def by metis

lemma theorem24_subformula :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. finite (α_el T)) ∧ finite 𝒯"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_off T) M 0"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_on T) M 0"
  and invarinf: "⋀p s. validinfpath M s p ⟹ P s (inf p) =  (∀T ∈ 𝒯. (∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p)))))"
  and locking: "⋀s. locked M B s = (∀ T ∈ 𝒯. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e)"
  and exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e " 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦ν ⋀⇩μT ∈ 𝒯. φ_on T ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (- α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (φ_off T ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (α_el T - α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)⟧ M e
    = ((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e))
  ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))"
  apply (simp add: assms del: Diamond.simps occurssimps locking)
proof 
  assume "∃S'. S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')}) ∧ s ∈ S'"
  then obtain S' where "s ∈ S' ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. S' ⊆ {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')})" by blast
  moreover have "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')} ⊆ {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T -α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))}" by (subst lemma50; (subst notdependshiftdown)?; simp; simp add: assms)
  ultimately have assum1: "S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))}) ∧ s ∈ S'" by blast
  let ?S' = "S' ∩ {s'. ∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)}"
  have "∀s ∈ ?S'. ∀T ∈ 𝒯. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)))"
    apply (rule ballI)+
  proof
    fix s T
    assume assum2: "s ∈ ?S'"
    hence "s ∈ S'" by auto
    moreover assume "T ∈ 𝒯"
    moreover assume "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
    ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T ∧ a' ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S'))" using assum1 by auto
    then obtain p s' where validpath: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T ∧ a' ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S'))" using assum1 by presburger
    moreover have "enabled M s' α⇩e ⟹ False" using assum2 validpath by auto
    moreover {
      assume s'inS' : "s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e"
      hence "occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)" using validpath notoccursendpath by metis
      moreover have "∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)" 
      proof
        assume "∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)"
        then obtain p' s'' where "validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)" by auto
        hence "validfinpath M s (p @ p') s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p @ p')) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)" using validpath addpathsnotoccurs by metis
        thus False using assum2 by blast
      qed
      ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)" using validpath s'inS' by auto
    }
    moreover {
      assume "∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T ∧ a' ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S'"
      then obtain a' s'' where s''inS': "a' ∈ α_el T ∧ a' ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S'" by auto
      hence "validfinpath M s' [(s', a', s'')] s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin ([(s', a', s'')])) ∧ occurs (α_el T) (fin (p @ [(s', a', s'')]))" by auto
      hence validaddpath : "validfinpath M s (p @ [(s', a', s'')]) s'' ∧  ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p @ [(s', a', s'')])) ∧ occurs (α_el T) (fin (p @ [(s', a', s'')]))" using validpath validfinpathsplit addpathsnotoccurs by metis 
      moreover have "∄p s'. validfinpath M s'' p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e)" 
      proof
        assume "∃p s'. validfinpath M s'' p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e)"
        then obtain p' s''' where "validfinpath M s'' p' s''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ (locked M B s''' ∨ enabled M s''' α⇩e)" by auto
        hence "validfinpath M s ((p @ [(s', a', s'')]) @ p') s''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin ((p @ [(s', a', s'')]) @ p')) ∧ (locked M B s''' ∨ enabled M s''' α⇩e)" using validaddpath addpathsnotoccurs by metis
        thus False using assum2 by blast
      qed
      ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ occurs (α_el T) (fin p)" using s''inS' by blast
    }
    ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p))" by blast
  qed
  moreover have "⋀s. s ∈ ?S' ⟹ ¬locked M B s" 
    apply (subgoal_tac "validfinpath M s [] s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin [])")
    apply blast
    apply simp
    done
  moreover have negnegT : "-(-𝒯) = 𝒯" by auto
  ultimately have "s ∈ ?S' ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ (∀T ∈ -(-𝒯). ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p))))))"
    apply (subst constructfairpath; (subst negnegT)?)
    using exclusive apply blast
    using persistent apply blast
    using assms(1) apply blast+
    using locking apply meson
    using persistent assms(1) apply blast+
    done
  hence "s ∈ ?S' ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)" using invarinf by blast
  thus "((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e))
  ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))" using assum1 by blast
next
  let ?S' = "{s. (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e))
  ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p))}"
  assume "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e))
  ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p))"
  hence "s ∈ ?S'" by simp
  moreover have "?S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?S')))})"
    apply (rule subsetI INT_I CollectI impI)+
  proof-
    fix s T
    assume assum1: "s ∈ ?S'"
    assume assum2 : "T ∈ 𝒯"
    assume assum3 : "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e" 
    show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?S'))"
    proof-
      have "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e)) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p))" using assum1 by auto
      moreover {
        assume "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e)"
        hence "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ enabled M s' α⇩e)" by auto
        moreover {
          assume "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'"
          then obtain p s' where assum4: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'" by auto
          moreover have "occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)"
            apply (rule ccontr)
            apply (subgoal_tac "s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e")
            using locking persistent assum2 assum3 assum4 apply blast+
            done
          ultimately have assum4: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s' ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p))" by auto
          moreover {
            assume "occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)"
            hence "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃ n ∈ indicespath (fin p). target (ind n (fin p)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e)" using occursstatealternative by metis
            hence "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃ n < length p. target (p!n) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e)" by simp
            moreover have "s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ validfinpath M s [] s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin [])  ∧ s ∈ ?S' ∩ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e" using assum1 by simp
            moreover {
              assume "∃ n < length p. target (p!n) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e"
              then obtain n where "n < length p ∧ target (p!n) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e" by auto
              hence "validfinpath M (target (p!n)) (drop (Suc n) p) s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (drop (Suc n) p)) ∧ locked M B s' ∧ validfinpath M s (take (Suc n) p) (target (p!n)) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (take (Suc n) p)) ∧ target (p!n) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e" 
                using assum4 validfinsubpathtargetright notoccursfinright occursfinleft validfinsubpathtarget by metis
              hence "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p)  ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∩ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e" by auto
            }
            ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p)  ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∩ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e" by blast
          }
          moreover {
            assume "occurs (α_el T) (fin p)"
            then obtain n where "n < length p ∧ action (p!n) ∈ α_el T" using occursfinalternative by blast
            hence "validfinpath M (target (p!n)) (drop (Suc n) p) s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (drop (Suc n) p)) ∧ locked M B s' ∧ validfinpath M s (take n p) (source (p!n)) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (take n p)) ∧ (source (p!n), action (p!n), target (p!n)) ∈ transition M ∧ action (p!n) ∈ α_el T ∧ action (p!n) ∉ α⇩f" 
              using assum4 validfinsubpath validfinsubpathtargetright notoccursfinright occursfinleft occursfinalternative ithtransitionfinpath splittransition by metis
            hence "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p)  ∧ (∃a s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ s'' ∈ ?S')" by blast
          }
        ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ ((s' ∈ ?S' ∩ (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e)) ∨ (∃a s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ s'' ∈ ?S'))" 
          by meson
        }
        ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T ∧ a ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?S'))" by blast
      }
      moreover {
        assume "∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)"
        then obtain p where predP: "validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p))))))" using invarinf by auto
        moreover from this have "source (p 0) = s ∧ suffix 0 p = p" by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
        ultimately have validinfpath: "validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (inf p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (inf p))" using assum2 assum3 by metis
        then obtain i where sourceoraction : "source (p i) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ action (p i) ∈ α_el T" using infpathoccursoroccursstate by metis
        have "⋀j. source (p j) ∈ ?S'"
        proof-
          fix j
          have "validinfpath M (source (p j)) (suffix j p) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (suffix j p)) ∧ P (source (p j)) (inf (suffix j p))"
          proof-
            have "(∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀k. (source ((suffix j p) k)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix k (suffix j p))) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source ((suffix j p) k)) (inf (suffix k (suffix j p)))))))" using predP by simp
            moreover have "validinfpath M (source (p j)) (suffix j p) ∧  ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (suffix j p))" using predP by auto
            ultimately show ?thesis using invarinf by metis
          qed
          thus "source (p j) ∈ ?S'" by blast
        qed
        moreover have "target (p i) = source (p (Suc i))" using predP by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
        ultimately have "source (p i) ∈ ?S' ∧ target (p i) ∈ ?S'" by auto
        moreover have "validfinpath M s (prefix i p) (source (p i)) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (prefix i p)) ∧ action (p i) ∉ α⇩f" using validinfpath validinfsubpath by auto
        moreover have "(source (p i), action (p i), target (p i)) ∈ transition M" using validinfpath splittransition validinfpath_def by metis
        ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (s' ∈ ?S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T ∧ a ∉ α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?S'))" using sourceoraction by blast
      }
      ultimately show ?thesis by blast
    qed
  qed
  ultimately obtain S' where "S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))}) ∧ s ∈ S'" by blast
  hence "s ∈ S' ∧ (∀T∈𝒯. S' ⊆ {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e ∨ (∃s'' a. a ∈ α_el T - α⇩f ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))}) ∧ s ∈ S'" by blast
  moreover have "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ {s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (enabled M s' α⇩e ∨ (s' ∈ S' ∧ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) ∨ (∃s'' a'. a' ∈ α_el T -α⇩f ∧ (s', a', s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ S')))} ⊆ {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')}" by (subst lemma50; (subst notdependshiftdown)?; simp; simp add: assms)
  ultimately have "S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')}) ∧ s ∈ S'" by blast
  thus "∃S'. S' ⊆ (⋂T∈𝒯. {s. s ∈ ⟦φ_on T⟧ M (newenvironment e S') ⟶ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' (φ_off T) (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ((α_el T) - α⇩f)) (var 0)))⟧ M (newenvironment e S')}) ∧ s ∈ S'" by blast
qed

lemma predPsubpath: 
  assumes invariant: "⋀p s. validpath M s p ⟹ P s p = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  shows "validpath M (target t) p ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ P (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p) ⟹ P (target t) p"
proof-
  assume assum1: "validpath M (target t) p ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ P (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p)"
  hence "validpath M (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p) ∧ P (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p)" by (cases p; auto)
  hence "∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p) (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p)" using invariant by auto
  hence "∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes (target t) p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p)" by auto
  thus "P (target t) p" using invariant assum1 by auto
qed

lemma predPsuperpath:
  assumes invariant: "⋀p s. validpath M s p ⟹ P s p = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  shows "validpath M (target t) p ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ P (target t) p ⟹ P (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p)"
proof-
  assume assum1: "validpath M (target t) p ∧ t ∈ transition M ∧ P (target t) p"
  hence allsuffixes: "∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes (target t) p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p)" using invariant by auto
  moreover {
    fix T
    assume Tintasks: "T ∈ 𝒯"
    moreover have "validfinpath M (source t) [t] (target t)" using assum1 by auto
    moreover assume "source t ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
    ultimately have "occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source t) (fin [t]) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin [t]) ∨ target t ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e" using persistent by blast
    hence "occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source t) (fin [t]) ∨ occurs (α_el T) (fin [t]) ∨ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (laststate (source t) [t]) p" using allsuffixes Tintasks unfolding allsuffixes_def by auto
    hence "occurs (α_el T) (extendfinpath [t] p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p)" using occursleftorright by metis
  }
  ultimately have "∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p) (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p)" by auto
  moreover have "validpath M (source t) (extendfinpath [t] p)" using assum1 by (cases p; auto)
  ultimately show ?thesis using invariant by blast
qed

lemma predPsubpathsuperpath :
  assumes invariant: "⋀p s. validpath M s p ⟹ P s p = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  shows "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ validpath M s' p' ⟹ P s (extendfinpath p p') = P s' p'"
  apply (rule P_extendpath[of M P]; simp?)
  apply (rule iffI)
  apply (rule predPsubpath[OF invariant]; simp)
  apply (rule predPsuperpath[OF invariant persistent])
  apply auto
  done
                                 
lemma feasible : 
  assumes invarinf: "⋀p s. validinfpath M s p ⟹ P s (inf p) =  ((∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p)))))))"
  and locking: "⋀s. locked M B s = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e)"
  and exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e " 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  and reachable: "⋀T s. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)))"
  and "finite 𝒯"
  shows "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ P s (inf p))"
proof-
  let ?S' = "{s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ locked M B s'}"
  have "s ∈ ?S' ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs {} (inf p) ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p))))))"
    apply (subst constructfairpath [where ?S'="?S'"])
    using exclusive persistent apply blast+
    defer
    using assms(6) apply simp
    apply simp
    using locking validfinpath.simps(1) apply metis
    apply simp
    apply simp
    apply (rule ballI impI)+
  proof-
    fix s'' T
    assume assum1: "s'' ∈ ?S'"
    assume "T ∈ 𝒯"
    moreover assume "s'' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
    ultimately obtain p s' where "validfinpath M s'' p s' ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s'' (fin p))" using reachable by blast
    moreover from this have "s' ∈ ?S'" using assum1 by (subst notlocked; auto)
    ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s'' p s' ∧ s' ∈ ?S' ∧ ¬occurs {} (fin p) ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s'' (fin p))" by (simp; blast)
  qed
  hence "s ∈ ?S' ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ P s (inf p)" using invarinf by blast
  thus ?thesis by auto
qed

lemma invarinf :
  assumes invariant: "⋀p s. validpath M s p ⟹ P s p =  (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  shows "validinfpath M s p ⟹ P s (inf p) =  ((∀T ∈ 𝒯. ((∀i. (source (p i)) ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ (occurs (α_el T) (inf (suffix i p)) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) (source (p i)) (inf (suffix i p)))))))"
  by (simp add: allsuffixes_validinfpath invariant)

lemma theorem24_feasible :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. finite (α_el T)) ∧ finite 𝒯"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_off T) M 0"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_on T) M 0"
  and invariant: "⋀s p. validpath M s p ⟹ P s p = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  and locking: "⋀s. locked M B s = (∀ T ∈ 𝒯. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e)"
  and exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e " 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  and feasible: "⋀s. (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ P s (inf p))"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⋀⇩μT ∈ 𝒯. φ_on T ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (- α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (φ_off T ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (α_el T -α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s p)"
  apply (subst negformula)
  apply (subst Diamondmatch)
  apply (subst theorem24_subformula; (rule invarinf[OF invariant] assms; auto)?)
  apply (subst splitviolating_predicate)
proof-
  {
    fix p
    have "⋀s p' s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ validpath M s' p' ⟹ P s (extendfinpath p p') = P s' p'"
      by (subst predPsubpathsuperpath [where ?p=p]; (rule assms)?; auto)
  }
  hence res1: "⋀s s' p p'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ validpath M s' p' ⟹ P s (extendfinpath p p') = P s' p'" by blast
  thus "⋀p p' s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ validpath M s' p' ⟹ P s' p' = P s (extendfinpath p p')" by blast  
  have "⋀s. (∃p. validpath M s p ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s p) =
    ((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s' ∨ enabled M s' α⇩e))
    ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))"
    apply (subst freeuntiloccurrenceprogressing_lockedenabled_pred[of _ B])
    apply (rule feasible)
    using res1 apply blast
    apply (subst invariant; simp add: locking exclusive)
    apply auto
    done
  thus "(∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ ((∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s' (inf p)))) =
      (∄p p' s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ validpath M s' p' ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p' α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s' p')" by blast
qed

theorem theorem24 :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ (∀T ∈ 𝒯. finite (α_el T)) ∧ finite 𝒯"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_off T) M 0"
  and "⋀T. T ∈ 𝒯 ⟹ ¬dependvar (φ_on T) M 0"
  and invariant: "⋀s p. P s p = (∀T ∈ 𝒯. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟶ occurs (α_el T) p ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s p))" 
  and locking: "⋀s. locked M B s = (∀ T ∈ 𝒯. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e)"
  and exclusive: "⋀s T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e " 
  and persistent: "⋀s p s' T. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ∧ (¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)  ∧ ¬occurs (α_el T) (fin p)) ⟹ s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e"
  and reachable: "⋀T s. T ∈ 𝒯 ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on T) 0⟧ M e ⟹ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (occurs (α_el T) (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (φ_off T) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p)))" 
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⋀⇩μT ∈ 𝒯. φ_on T ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (φ_off T ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (α_el T -α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s p)"
  apply (rule theorem24_feasible[OF assms(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7)]; blast?)
  apply (rule feasible[OF invarinf locking exclusive persistent]; blast?)
  using invariant reachable assms(1) apply blast+
  done

subsection ‹Corollaries›

lemma WFA_invariant: "WFA M B s p = (∀a∈ -B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ enabledactions M s ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p ∨ occursstate {s. a ∉ enabledactions M s} s p))"
proof-
  have "WFA M B s p = (∀a ∈ -B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ perpetuallyenabled M s p ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p))" unfolding WFA_def allsuffixes_def by auto
  moreover have "⋀a s p. (a ∈ perpetuallyenabled M s p ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p) = (a ∈ enabledactions M s ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p ∨ occursstate {s. a ∉ enabledactions M s} s p)" by (auto simp: perpetuallyenabled_def occursstate_def)
  ultimately show ?thesis by simp
qed

corollary corollary25 :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⋀⇩μa∈- B. ⟨a⟩⇩μtt ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ ([a]⇩μff ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts ({a} -α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ WFA M B s p)"
  apply (rule theorem24)
  apply (simp add: assms notoccursnotdepends)+
  apply (simp add: WFA_invariant occurs_def)
  apply (simp add: locked_def; blast)
  apply simp
proof-
  fix a s
  assume "a ∈ -B ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e"
  then obtain s' where "(s, a, s') ∈ transition M" by auto
  hence "validfinpath M s [(s, a, s')] s' ∧ occurs {a} (fin [(s, a, s')])" by auto
  thus "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (occurs {a} (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown (box a ff) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p))" by blast
next
  fix s p s' a
  assume "a ∈ -B ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown (box a ff) 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs {a} (fin p)"
  hence "s' ∉ ⟦shiftdown (box a ff) 0⟧ M e" using notoccursendpath by metis
  thus "s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e" by simp
qed

lemma lockedphion_WHFA: "finite (-B) ⟹ locked M B s = (∀a∈ -B. s ∉ ⟦⟨Acts (-B)⇧⋆⟩⇩R ⟨a⟩⇩μ tt⟧ M e)"
  apply (simp only: Diamondreachable)
proof-
  have "locked M B s = WHFA M B s (fin [])" by (simp only: WHFAempty)
  thus "locked M B s = (∀a∈-B. a ∉ reachableactions M B s)" by (auto simp: WHFA_def perpetuallyreachable_def)
qed

lemma WHFA_invariant: "finite (-B) ⟹ WHFA M B s p = (∀a∈-B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e ⟶ occurs {a} p ∨ occursstate (⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e) s p))"
  apply (simp only: Diamondreachable)
  using Boxnotreachable
proof-
  assume assum1: "finite (-B)"
  hence "⋀s' a.  s'∈ ⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e =  (a ∉ reachableactions M B s')" by (simp only: Boxnotreachable)
  hence occursnotreachable: "⋀a s p. occursstate (⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e) s p = (occursstate {s. a ∉ reachableactions M B s} s p)" unfolding occursstate_def by blast
  have "WHFA M B s p = (∀a ∈ -B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ perpetuallyreachable M B s p ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p))" unfolding WHFA_def allsuffixes_def by auto
  moreover have "⋀a s p. (a ∈ perpetuallyreachable M B s p ⟶ a ∈ alloccurringactions p) = (a ∈ reachableactions M B s ⟶ occurs {a} p ∨ occursstate {s. a ∉ reachableactions M B s} s p)" by (auto simp: occurs_def perpetuallyreachable_def occursstate_def)
  ultimately have "WHFA M B s p = (∀a∈-B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ reachableactions M B s ⟶ occurs {a} p ∨ occursstate {s. a ∉ reachableactions M B s} s p))" by simp
  thus "WHFA M B s p = (∀a∈-B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ reachableactions M B s ⟶ occurs {a} p ∨ occursstate (⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e) s p))" apply (subst occursnotreachable) by simp
qed

corollary corollary26 :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⋀⇩μa∈-B. ⟨Acts (-B)⇧⋆⟩⇩R ⟨a⟩⇩μtt ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ ([Acts (-B)⇧⋆]⇩R [a]⇩μff ∧⇩μ var 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts ({a} -α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ WHFA M B s p)"
  apply (rule theorem24; (simp only: shiftdownDiamond shiftdownBox shiftdown.simps)?; (rule WHFA_invariant lockedphion_WHFA)?)
  apply (simp add: assms notoccursnotdepends del: Diamond.simps Box.simps)+  using Boxnotreachable Diamondreachable assms apply meson
proof-
  fix s p s' a
  assume "a ∈ -B ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs {a} (fin p)"
  hence "s' ∉ ⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e" using notoccursendpath by meson
  hence "s' ∈ ⟦neg (Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff))⟧ M e" by simp
  moreover have "⟦neg (box a ff)⟧ M e = ⟦diamond a tt⟧ M e" by auto
  ultimately show "s' ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e" using negBox Diamond_eq by metis
next
  fix a s
  assume "a ∈ - B ∧ s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e"
  hence "a ∈ reachableactions M B s" by (simp only: Diamondreachable assms)
  then obtain p s' s'' where "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M" by (auto simp: reachableactionsdef)
  hence "validfinpath M s (p@[(s', a, s'')]) s'' ∧ occurs {a} (fin (p@[(s', a, s'')]))" by simp
  thus "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (occurs {a} (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e) s (fin p))" by blast
qed

lemma JA_invariant:
"JA M con B s p = (∀a∈-B. allsuffixes s p (λs p. a ∈ enabledactions M s ⟶ occurs {a'. ¬con a a'} p))"
  unfolding JA_def occurs_def allsuffixes_def by blast

corollary corollary27 :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B) ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. finite {a'. ¬con a a'})"
  and "concurrency M con"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ⟩⇩R (ν ⋀⇩μa∈- B. ⟨a⟩⇩μtt ⟹⇩R ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts ({a'. ¬con a a'} - α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ JA M con B s p)"
proof-
  have "⟦neg (Diamond ρ (nu (And (-B) (λa. or (neg (diamond a tt)) (Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (Diamond (Acts ({a'. ¬ con a a'} -α⇩f)) (var 0))))))))⟧ M e =
    ⟦neg (Diamond ρ (nu (And (-B) (λa. or (neg (diamond a tt)) (Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' ff (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ({a'. ¬ con a a'} -α⇩f)) (var 0))))))))⟧ M e"
    by (simp add: assms(1) Diamond_eq)
  moreover have "s ∈ ⟦neg (Diamond ρ (nu (And (-B) (λa. or (neg (diamond a tt)) (Diamond (Star (Acts (-α⇩f))) (or (or (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt) (and' ff (var 0))) (Diamond (Acts ({a'. ¬ con a a'} -α⇩f)) (var 0))))))))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ JA M con B s p)"
    apply (rule theorem24)
    apply (simp add: assms notoccursnotdepends)+
    apply (simp add: occursstate_def JA_invariant)
    apply (simp add: locked_def; blast)
    apply simp
  proof-
    fix a s
    assume "a ∈ -B ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e"
    then obtain s' where "(s, a, s') ∈ transition M" by auto
    moreover have "¬con a a" using assms(2) by (simp add: concurrency_def irreflp_def)
    ultimately have "validfinpath M s [(s, a, s')] s' ∧ occurs {a'. ¬con a a'} (fin [(s, a, s')])" by auto
    thus "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (occurs {a'. ¬con a a'} (fin p) ∨ occursstate (⟦shiftdown ff 0⟧ M e) s (fin p))" by blast
  next
    fix s p s' a
    have "validfinpath M s p s' ⟶ enabledactions M s ∩ preimagerelation con (alloccurringactions (fin p)) ⊆ enabledactions M s'" using assms(2) by (auto simp: concurrency_def)
    moreover assume "a ∈ - B ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e ∧ ¬occursstate (⟦shiftdown ff 0⟧ M e) s (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs {a'. ¬con a a'} (fin p)"
    ultimately have "a ∈ enabledactions M s'" by auto
    thus "s' ∈ ⟦shiftdown (diamond a tt) 0⟧ M e" by simp
  qed
  ultimately show ?thesis by blast
qed

subsection ‹Theorems ‹SFA› and ‹SHFA››

lemma freeenabledpath : 
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ f)⟧ M e =
    (s ∈ ⟦⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R f⟧ M e ∨ 
       (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ enabled M s' α⇩e))" 
  apply (subst Diamondor)
proof-
  have "s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt)⟧ M e = 
    (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) p ∧ s' ∈ ⟦Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt⟧ M e)" by (rule Diamondmatch)
  moreover have "... = (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ enabled M s' α⇩e)" by (subst Diamond_enabled; (subst matchstaract)?; auto simp: assms)
  ultimately show "(s ∈ ⟦or (Diamond (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) (Diamond (Acts α⇩e) tt)) (Diamond (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) f)⟧ M e) = 
    (s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) f⟧ M e ∨ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ enabled M s' α⇩e))" unfolding formulasemantics.simps by blast
qed

lemma musubformula:
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) "
  shows "s ∈ ⟦μ var (Suc 0) ∧⇩μ (⟨a⟩⇩μvar (Suc 0) ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)⟧ M e =
  (∃p s' s''. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ e 0 ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ e 0)"
  by (subst proposition40; (rule notoccursnotdepends)?; simp add: assms; auto; blast)

lemma alwaysnextaction_pred: "validinfpath M s p ∧ a ∈ {a. allsuffixes s (inf p) (λs p. ∃s ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q s a)} ⟹∃n>m. Q (source (p n)) a"
proof-
  fix m
  assume assum1: "validinfpath M s p ∧ a ∈ {a. allsuffixes s (inf p) (λs p. ∃s ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q s a)}"
  hence "∃s ∈ insert (target (p m)) {target (p (Suc m + i)) | i. True}. Q s a" by (auto simp: allsuffixes_def)
  hence "∃s ∈ {target (p i) | i. i ≥ m}. Q s a" using nat_le_iff_add Suc_leD by blast
  then obtain n where "n ≥ m ∧ Q (target (p n)) a" by auto
  hence "Suc n > m ∧ Q (source (p (Suc n))) a" using assum1 by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
  thus "∃n>m. Q (source (p n)) a" by blast
qed

lemma relentlessly_subpath': 
  assumes "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "validinfpath M s p  ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (inf p) ⊆ X ∧ a ∈ A s (inf p)"
  shows "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'"
proof-
  have "∃n>0. Q a (source (p n))" using assms by (subst alwaysnextaction_pred; auto) 
  then obtain n where "Q a (source (p n))" by auto
  moreover have "validfinpath M s (prefix n p) (source (p n)) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (prefix n p)) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (prefix n p)) ⊆ X " using assms by auto
  ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'" by blast
qed

lemma notreachable_validpath: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs B (fin p) ∧ a ∉ reachableactions M B s ⟹ a ∉ reachableactions M B s'"
proof-
  assume assum1: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs B (fin p) ∧ a ∉ reachableactions M B s"
  hence "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs B (fin p) ∧ s ∈ {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs B (fin p) ∧ a ∈ enabledactions M s'}" by (simp add: reachableactions_def reachableactionsset_def)
  hence "s' ∈ {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs B (fin p) ∧ a ∈ enabledactions M s'}" by (subst notlockedoccurs[of s M B _ p]; simp)
  thus ?thesis by (simp add: reachableactions_def reachableactionsset_def)
qed

lemma constructPpath :
  assumes "finite (-B)"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ⟹ a ∈ reachableactions M B s" 
  and "⋀s. (∀a ∈ -B. ¬Q a s) ⟹ locked M B s"
  and "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "P = (λs p. allsuffixes s p (λs p. A s p -B ⊆ alloccurringactions p))"
  and "⋀s a. s ∈ X ∧ a ∈ α⇩f -B ⟹ ¬Q a s"
  and "S' = {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'}"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ∧ s ∈ X ⟹ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))"
  shows "s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)"
proof-
  assume assum2: "s ∈ S' ∩ X"
  have "⋀s. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ (∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')))"
    apply (rule inductfiniteset[where ?A="-B"])
    using assms(1) apply simp
  proof-
    fix s 
    assume "s ∈ S' ∩ X" 
    hence "s ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s [] s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin []) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin []) ⊆ X" by simp
    thus "∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬ occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a∈{}. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" by blast
  next
    fix s a A'
    assume assum3: "s ∈ S' ∩ X"
    assume "a ∈ -B - A' ∧ (∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬ occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a∈A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')))"
    then obtain p s' where IH : "a ∈ -B - A' ∧ s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬ occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a∈A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" by auto
    have "(∃p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'') ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')" by blast
    moreover {
      assume "∃p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''"
      then obtain p' s'' where firstpath: "validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''" by auto
      hence "s'' ∈ alloccurringstates s' (fin p')" using laststateoccurs by metis
      hence enabledaction: "a ∈ -B ∧ s'' ∈ X ∧ Q a s''" using firstpath IH by auto
      then obtain p'' s''' s'''' where "validfinpath M s'' p'' s''' ∧ alloccurringstates s'' (fin p'') ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p'') ∧ (s''', a, s'''') ∈ transition M ∧ s'''' ∈ X" using assms(8) by blast
      moreover have "a ∈ -α⇩f" using enabledaction assms(6) by auto
      ultimately have secondpath: "validfinpath M s'' (p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]) s'''' ∧ alloccurringstates s'' (fin (p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]))"  by auto
      hence validpath: "validfinpath M s' (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]) s'''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ⊆ X ∧ a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]))" using firstpath secondpath by auto
      hence "s ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]) s'''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ⊆ X ∧ a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]))" using assum3 IH by auto
      moreover have "∀a' ∈ A'. a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s'''' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s'')"
      proof
        fix a' 
        assume "a' ∈ A'"
        hence "a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s'')" using IH by blast
        moreover have "a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ⟹ a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]))" by auto
        moreover { 
          assume assum1: "∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s''"
          have "∄p' s''. validfinpath M s'''' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧  alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s''"
          proof (rule ccontr)
            assume "¬(∄p' s''. validfinpath M s'''' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧  alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s'')"
            then obtain p''' s where "validfinpath M s'''' p''' s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p''') ∧  alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p''') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s" by blast
            hence "validfinpath M s' (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]@p''') s ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]@p''')) ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin (p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]@p''')) ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s" using validpath by auto
            thus False using assum1 by blast
          qed
        }
        ultimately show "a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s'''' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧  alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s'')" by blast
      qed
      ultimately have validfinalpath: "s ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]) s'''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a' ∈ insert a A'. a' ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s'''' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧  alloccurringstates s'''' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a' s''))" by simp
      moreover {
        from this have "alloccurringstates s (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')])) ⊆ S'" apply (subst allnextstatesnotlocked[of S' M α⇩f "λs. locked M B s" _ _ s'''']) using assms(7) by auto
        moreover have "s'''' ∈ alloccurringstates s (fin (p@p'@p''@[(s''', a, s'''')]))" using validfinalpath laststateoccurs by metis
        ultimately have "s'''' ∈ S'" by simp
      }
      ultimately have "∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a∈insert a A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" by meson
    }
    moreover {
      assume "∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''"
      moreover have "∀a ∈ A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')" using IH by blast
      ultimately have "s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ insert a A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" using IH by auto
      hence "∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ insert a A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions  (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧  alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" by meson
    }
    ultimately show "∃p s'. s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a∈insert a A'. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin p) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" by blast
  qed
  hence "∀s. ∃succ. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟶ (∃s' ∈ S'. validfinpath M s succ s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin succ) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin succ) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin succ) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')))" by meson
  hence "∃succ. ∀s ∈ S' ∩ X. (∃s' ∈ S'. validfinpath M s (succ s) s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (succ s)) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (succ s)) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s)) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')))" by (rule succswitch)
  then obtain succ where succ: "∀s ∈ S'∩ X. (∃s' ∈ S'. validfinpath M s (succ s) s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (succ s)) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (succ s)) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s)) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'')))" by auto
  have notempty: "⋀s. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ succ s ≠ [] ∧ laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s) ∈ S' ∩ X"
  proof
    fix s
    assume inS': "s ∈ S' ∩ X"
    then obtain s' where assum1: "s' ∈ S' ∧ validfinpath M s (succ s) s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (succ s)) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin (succ s)) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s)) ∨ (∄p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''))" using succ by meson
    hence s'inX: "s' ∈ X" using assum1 laststateoccurs subset_iff by metis
    show "succ s ≠ []"
    proof
      assume emptypath: "succ s = []"
      have "∀a ∈ -B. ¬Q a s'"
      proof
        fix a
        have "a ∉ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s))" using emptypath by simp
        moreover assume "a ∈ -B"
        ultimately have notreachable: "⋀p' s''. validfinpath M s' p' s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin p') ⊆ X ⟹ ¬Q a s''" using assum1 by blast
        thus "¬Q a s'" using s'inX by (subst notreachable[where ?p'="[]" and ?s''="s'"]; auto)
      qed
      hence "validfinpath M s' [] s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin []) ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin ([])) ⊆ X ∧ locked M B s'" by (auto simp: assms(3) s'inX)
      thus False using assms(7) inS' assum1 by blast
    qed
    hence "s' = laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s)" using assum1 laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive validfinpathlaststate by metis
    thus "laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s) ∈ S' ∩ X" using s'inX assum1 by auto
  qed
  let ?p="recursiveconcpaths succ s"
  have validpath: "⋀s. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ validinfpath M s (recursiveconcpaths succ s)"
    apply (rule validinfpathconc[where ?S'="S' ∩ X"]; rule conjI)
    apply simp
    apply (rule ballI conjI)+
    using notempty apply simp
  proof
    fix s
    assume assum1: "s ∈ S' ∩ X"
    thus "validfinpath M s (succ s) (laststate s (succ s))" using succ validfinpathlaststate by metis
    thus "laststate s (succ s) ∈ S' ∩ X" using assum1 notempty by (simp add: laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive)
  qed
  have "⋀s. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ ∀n. action (recursiveconcpaths succ s n) ∉ α⇩f ∧ target (recursiveconcpaths succ s n) ∈ X"
    apply (rule validpredconc [where ?S'="S' ∩ X" and ?Q="λs p. ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X"])
    apply simp
    apply auto[1]
    using notempty succ apply meson
    done
  hence alphaffreeandX: "⋀s. s ∈ S' ∩ X ⟹ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ s)) ∧ alloccurringstates s (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ s)) ⊆ X" unfolding occursinfalternative by (subst alloccurringstatesinset; auto)
  have "⋀s. s∈S' ∩ X ⟹ P s (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ s))" 
    apply (rule P_alternative [of A Q])
    apply (simp add: assms)
    apply (simp add: assms)
  proof-
    fix s n a
    assume inS': "s∈S' ∩ X"
    assume inBcomp: "a ∈ A (target (recursiveconcpaths succ s n)) (inf (suffix (Suc n) (recursiveconcpaths succ s))) -B"
    hence "∃s' p. s' ∈ S' ∩ X ∧ a ∈ A s' (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ s')) ∧ suffix (Suc n) (recursiveconcpaths succ s) = conc p (recursiveconcpaths succ s')" 
      apply (subst suffix_recursiveconcpathsrelentlessly[OF assms(4)]) 
      apply (rule conjI)
      using inS' apply blast
      apply (rule conjI)
      using notempty succ apply meson
      apply simp+
      done
    then obtain p s' where subpath: "s' ∈ S' ∩ X ∧ a ∈ A s' (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ s')) ∧ suffix (Suc n) (recursiveconcpaths succ s) = conc p (recursiveconcpaths succ s')" by blast
    obtain s'' where subsubpath: "validfinpath M s' (succ s') s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (succ s')) ∧ alloccurringstates s' (fin (succ s')) ⊆ X ∧ (∀a ∈ -B. a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s')) ∨ (∄p' s'''. validfinpath M s'' p' s''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s'' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'''))" using succ subpath by meson
    moreover from this have laststate1: "s'' = laststate s' (succ s')" using validfinpathlaststate by metis
    moreover from this have laststate2: "laststate s' (succ s') = laststate_nonexhaustive (succ s')" using laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive subpath notempty by metis
    ultimately have "a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s')) ∨ (∄p' s'''. validfinpath M s'' p' s''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s'' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s''')" using inBcomp by blast
    moreover have unfoldrecursive: "recursiveconcpaths succ s' = conc (succ s') (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s')))" using subpath by (simp add: laststate_laststate_nonexhaustive notempty unfoldrecursiveconcpaths) 
    moreover {
      have "A s' (inf (conc (succ s') (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))))) = A s'' (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))))" by (rule relentlessly_infextendpath[OF assms(4)])
      hence "a ∈ A s'' (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))))" using subpath unfoldrecursive by auto 
      hence "∃p' s'''. validfinpath M s'' p' s''' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p') ∧ alloccurringstates s'' (fin p') ⊆ X ∧ Q a s'''" 
        apply (subst relentlessly_subpath' [of A Q M _ "recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))"]; simp only: assms(4))
        using alphaffreeandX laststate1 laststate2 subpath validpath notempty by metis 
    }
    ultimately have "a ∈ alloccurringactions (fin (succ s'))" by blast
    hence "occurs {a} (fin (succ s'))" by auto
    hence "occurs {a} (extendfinpath p (extendfinpath (succ s') (inf (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))))))" by (subst occursright; (subst occursleft)?; simp)
    hence "a ∈ alloccurringactions (inf (conc p (conc (succ s') (recursiveconcpaths succ (laststate s' (succ s'))))))" unfolding extendfinpath.simps occurs_def by blast
    thus "a ∈ alloccurringactions (inf (suffix (Suc n) (recursiveconcpaths succ s)))" using subpath unfoldrecursive by metis
  qed
  thus "∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)" using assum2 validpath alphaffreeandX by blast
qed

lemma P_feasible :
  assumes "finite (-B)"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ⟹ a ∈ reachableactions M B s" 
  and "⋀s. (∀a ∈ -B. ¬Q a s) ⟹ locked M B s"
  and "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "P = (λs p. allsuffixes s p (λs p. A s p -B ⊆ alloccurringactions p))"
  shows "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ P s (inf p))"
proof-
  have "s ∈ {s. ∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs {} (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'} ∩ UNIV ⟹ ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs {} (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)"
    apply (rule constructPpath[of B Q M A P UNIV]; simp add: assms; blast?)
  proof-
    fix s a
    assume "a ∉ B ∧ Q a s"
    hence "a ∈ reachableactions M B s" using assms(2) by simp
    thus "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M)" unfolding reachableactions_def reachableactionsset_def enabledactions_def by blast
  qed
  thus ?thesis by auto
qed    

lemma Psubformula :
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite (-B)"
  and "⋀a. ¬dependvar (φ_on a) M 0"
  and "¬dependvar φ_off M 0"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ⟹ a ∈ reachableactions M B s" 
  and "⋀s. (∀a ∈ -B. ¬Q a s) ⟹ locked M B s"
  and "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "P = (λs p. allsuffixes s p (λs p. A s p -B ⊆ alloccurringactions p))"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ⟹ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on a) 0⟧ M e = Q a s"
  and "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e = (∀a ∈ α⇩f -B. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on a) 0⟧ M e)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆⟩⇩R (ν φ_off ∧⇩μ (⋀⇩μa∈- B. φ_on a ⟹⇩R (μ var 1 ∧⇩μ (⟨a⟩⇩μvar 1 ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (- α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0))))⟧ M e =
        ((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s')
        ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))"
  apply (simp add: assms Diamondmatch matchstaract musubformula And_eq_all Diamondreachable notdependshiftdown del: Diamond.simps Box.simps alloccurringmap.simps And_eq_all' occurssimps formulasemantics.simps(10) assms(7))
  apply (subst alloccursnotoccurs)
  apply (subst double_complement)
  apply (rule iffI impI)+
proof-
  assume "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃X⊆⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e. X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X)"
  then obtain p s' X where assum1: "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ X ⊆ ⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e ∧ X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ alloccurringstates s (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X" by auto
  let ?S' = "X ∩ {s'. ∄p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s''}"
  have "s' ∈ ?S' ∨ s' ∉ ?S'" by auto
  moreover {
    assume "s' ∈ ?S'"
    hence "∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s' (inf p)" 
      apply (subst constructPpath[of B Q M A P X])
      apply (simp add: assms)+
      using assum1 assms(8) assms(9) apply auto[1]
      apply simp
      using assum1 apply auto
      done
    then obtain p' where "validinfpath M s' p' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p') ∧ P s' (inf p')" by auto
    moreover have "validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p)" using assum1 by simp
    moreover have "⋀p'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ validinfpath M s' p' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p') ⟹ validinfpath M s (conc p p') ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (conc p p'))" by auto
    moreover have "validfinpath M s p s'  ⟹ P s' (inf p') = P s (inf (conc p p'))" by (subst relentlessly_extendpath[of A Q _ B M]; simp add: assms(6) assms(7))
