    ultimately have "∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)" by blast
  }
  moreover {
    assume "s' ∉ ?S'"
    then obtain p' s'' where "validfinpath M s (p@p') s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (p@p')) ∧ locked M B s''" using assum1 by auto
    hence "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'" by blast
  }
  ultimately show "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s')
        ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p))" by blast
next
  assume "(∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p))"
  moreover {
    assume assum1: "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'"
    let ?X = "{s. locked M B s}"
    have "⋀a s. a ∈ -B ∧ locked M B s ⟹ ¬Q a s"
    proof-
      fix a s
      assume "a ∈ -B ∧ locked M B s"
      hence "a ∈ -B ∧ a ∉ reachableactions M B s" by (simp add: lockednotreachable)
      thus "¬Q a s" using assms(4) by auto
    qed
    hence "?X⊆{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s} ∧ ?X⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ?X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ ?X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?X))}" by blast 
    hence "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃X⊆{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s}. X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X)" using assum1 by blast
  }
  moreover {
    assume "∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)" 
    then obtain p where assum1: "validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)" by auto
    have "∃n. allsuffixes (source (p n)) (inf (suffix n p)) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" by (subst somesuffix_onlyrelentlessly[where ?M="M" and ?s=s]; simp add: assms assum1)
    then obtain n where assum2: "allsuffixes (source (p n)) (inf (suffix n p)) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" by blast
    let ?X="{s. ∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p) ∧ allsuffixes s (inf p) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)}"
    have "?X⊆{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s}"
      apply (rule subsetI CollectI)+
    proof
      fix s a
      assume "s ∈ ?X"
      then obtain p where inX: "validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p) ∧ allsuffixes s (inf p) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" by auto
      assume inalphaf: "a ∈ α⇩f ∩ - B"
      show "¬Q a s"
      proof
        assume "Q a s"
        hence "a ∈ -B ∧ a ∈ A s (inf p)" using inX inalphaf unfolding allsuffixes_def by auto
        hence "a ∈ alloccurringactions (inf p)" using inX unfolding assms(7) allsuffixes_def by auto
        moreover have "a ∉ alloccurringactions (inf p)" using inX inalphaf by auto
        ultimately show False by simp
      qed
    qed
    moreover have "?X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ?X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ ?X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?X))}"
      apply (rule subsetI CollectI ballI)+
    proof
      fix s a
      assume "s ∈ ?X"
      then obtain p where inX: "validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p) ∧ allsuffixes s (inf p) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" by auto
      have allstatesinX: "alloccurringstates s (inf p) ⊆ ?X"
        unfolding alloccurringstatesalternative
      proof
        fix s'
        assume "s' ∈ insert s {target (ind i (inf p)) | i. i ∈ indicespath (inf p)}"
        hence "s' = s ∨ (∃i. s' = target (p i))" by auto
        moreover have "s' = s ⟹ s' ∈ ?X" using inX by auto
        moreover {
          assume "∃i. s' = target (p i)"
          then obtain i where s'eqtarget: "s' = target (p i)" by auto
          have "P s (inf p) = P (source (p (Suc i))) (inf (suffix (Suc i) p))" using inX by (subst relentlessly_infpathsuffix[OF assms(6) assms(7)]; blast)
          hence "P (source (p (Suc i))) (inf (suffix (Suc i) p))" using inX by simp
          moreover have "validinfpath M (source (p (Suc i))) (suffix (Suc i) p) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (suffix (Suc i) p)) ∧ allsuffixes (source (p (Suc i))) (inf (suffix (Suc i) p)) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" apply (subst suffixallsuffixesinf) using inX by auto
          ultimately have "validinfpath M (target (p i)) (suffix (Suc i) p) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (suffix (Suc i) p)) ∧ P (target (p i)) (inf (suffix (Suc i) p)) ∧ allsuffixes (target (p i)) (inf (suffix (Suc i) p)) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" using inX by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
          hence "s' ∈ ?X" using s'eqtarget by blast
        }
        ultimately show "s' ∈ ?X" by auto
      qed  
      assume inBcomp: "a ∈ - B"
      assume "Q a s"
      hence "a ∈ alloccurringactions (inf p)" using inBcomp inX unfolding assms(7) allsuffixes_def by auto
      then obtain i where actionieqa: "action (p i) = a" by auto
      have "alloccurringstates s (fin (prefix i p)) ⊆ alloccurringstates s (inf p)" by auto
      hence "s ∈ ?X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin (prefix i p)) ⊆ ?X" using allstatesinX by blast
      moreover have "validfinpath M s (prefix i p) (source (p i))" using inX validinfsubpath by metis
      moreover have "¬occurs α⇩f (fin (prefix i p))" using inX by auto
      moreover have "p i ∈ transition M" using inX by (simp add: validinfpath_def)
      moreover from this have "(source (p i), a, target (p i)) ∈ transition M ∧ target (p i) ∈ ?X" using allstatesinX actionieqa unfolding alloccurringstatesalternative by auto
      ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ ?X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ ?X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ ?X)" by blast
    qed
    moreover have "validfinpath M s (prefix n p) (source (p n)) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin (prefix n p))" using assum1 by auto
    moreover have "source (p n) ∈ ?X"
    proof
      have "P s (inf p) = P (source (p n)) (inf (suffix n p))" using assum1 by (subst relentlessly_infpathsuffix[OF assms(6) assms(7)]; blast)
      hence "P (source (p n)) (inf (suffix n p))" using assum1 by simp
      moreover have "validinfpath M (source (p n)) (suffix n p) ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf (suffix n p)) ∧ allsuffixes (source (p n)) (inf (suffix n p)) (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" using assum1 assum2 by auto
      ultimately show "∃p'. validinfpath M (source (p n)) p' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p') ∧ P (source (p n)) (inf p') ∧ allsuffixes (source (p n)) (inf p') (λs p. {a. Q a s} -B ⊆ A s p)" by blast
    qed
    ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃X⊆{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s}. X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X)" by blast
  }
  ultimately have "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃X⊆{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s}. X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X)" by blast
  moreover have "{s. ∀a∈α⇩f ∩ - B. ¬Q a s} = ⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e" using assms(8) assms(9) by auto 
  ultimately show "∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃X⊆⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e. X ⊆ {s. ∀a∈- B. Q a s ⟶ (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ s ∈ X ∧ alloccurringmap target (fin p) ⊆ X ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (∃s''. (s', a, s'') ∈ transition M ∧ s'' ∈ X))} ∧ s' ∈ X)" by auto
qed

lemma Pformula_withsubformula: 
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ⟹ a ∈ reachableactions M B s" 
  and "⋀s. (∀a ∈ -B. ¬Q a s) ⟹ locked M B s"
  and "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "P = (λs p. allsuffixes s p (λs p. A s p -B ⊆ alloccurringactions p))"
  and feasible : "⋀s. (∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ locked M B s') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ P s (inf p))"
  and subformula: "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (- α⇩f))) f⟧ M e =
        ((∃p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s')
        ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))" 
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ ⋅ (Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆)⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ f)⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s p)"
  apply (subst negformula)
  unfolding Diamond.simps(5) apply (subst Diamondmatch)
  apply (subst splitviolating_predicate)
  apply (rule relentlessly_extendpath[OF assms(4) assms(5)])
  unfolding validpath.simps apply blast
  apply (subst freeenabledpath)
  apply (simp add: assms)
  apply (subst subformula)
proof-
  have "⋀s. (∃p'. validpath M s p' ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p' α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s p') =
    ((∃p s''. validfinpath M s p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e))
    ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s (inf p)))"
    apply (rule freeuntiloccurrenceprogressing_lockedenabled_pred) 
    apply (rule feasible)
    apply (subst relentlessly_extendpath[OF assms(4) assms(5)], blast, simp)
    apply (subst relentlesslyinvarfin[OF assms(2) assms(3) assms(4) assms(5)]; simp)
    done
  hence "(∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ ((∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ (locked M B s'' ∨ enabled M s'' α⇩e)) ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s' (inf p)))) = 
    (∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ (∃p'. validpath M s' p' ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p' α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s' p'))" by blast
  thus "(∄p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ (((∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ locked M B s'') ∨ (∃p. validinfpath M s' p ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (inf p) ∧ P s' (inf p))) ∨ (∃p s''. validfinpath M s' p s'' ∧ ¬occurs α⇩f (fin p) ∧ enabled M s'' α⇩e))) = 
    (∄p p' s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ match ρ p ∧ validpath M s' p' ∧ freeuntiloccurrence p' α⇩f α⇩e ∧ P s' p')" by blast
qed

lemma Pformula : 
  assumes "⋀a. ¬dependvar (φ_on a) M 0"
  and "¬dependvar φ_off M 0"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ∧ Q a s ⟹ a ∈ reachableactions M B s" 
  and "⋀s. (∀a ∈ -B. ¬ Q a s) ⟹ locked M B s"
  and "A = (λs p. {a. allsuffixes s p (λs p. ∃s' ∈ alloccurringstates s p. Q a s')})"
  and "P = (λs p. allsuffixes s p (λs p. A s p -B ⊆ alloccurringactions p))"
  and "⋀s a. a ∈ -B ⟹ s ∈ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on a) 0⟧ M e = Q a s"
  and "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦shiftdown φ_off 0⟧ M e = (∀a ∈ α⇩f -B. s ∉ ⟦shiftdown (φ_on a) 0⟧ M e)"
  and "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ ⋅ (Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆)⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (ν φ_off ∧⇩μ (⋀⇩μa∈-B. φ_on a ⟹⇩R (μ var 1 ∧⇩μ (⟨a⟩⇩μvar 1 ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)))))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧  P s p)"
  apply (subst Pformula_withsubformula [OF assms(9, 3-6)]; (rule Psubformula [OF _ assms(1-8)])?; (simp add: assms(9))?)
  apply (rule P_feasible[OF _ assms(3-6)]; simp add: assms)
  done 

lemma finiteBcomp [simp]: "finite A ∨ finite (-B) ⟹ finite (A - B)"
proof-
  assume "finite A ∨ finite (-B)"
  hence "finite (A ∩ -B)" by simp
  moreover have "A ∩ -B = A - B" by auto
  ultimately show ?thesis by simp
qed

theorem SFAformula : 
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ ⋅ (Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆)⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (ν [Acts (α⇩f -B)]⇩R ff ∧⇩μ (⋀⇩μa ∈ -B. ⟨a⟩⇩μtt ⟹⇩R (μ var 1 ∧⇩μ (⟨a⟩⇩μ var 1 ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)))))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ SFA M B s p)"
  apply (rule Pformula[where ?Q="λa s. a ∈ enabledactions M s" and ?A="λs p. relentlesslyenabled M s p"]; (rule notoccursnotdepends)?; (simp only: assms(1))?)
  unfolding SFA_def
  apply simp
  apply simp
  using enabled_reachable subset_iff apply metis
  unfolding locked_def apply blast
  apply (simp add: relentlesslyenabled_def)+
  unfolding Boxmatch apply (subst matchunfoldActs, simp add: assms)
proof-
  fix s
  have "(∀p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (∃t. p = [t] ∧ action t ∈ α⇩f -B) ⟶ s' ∈ ⟦ff⟧ M e) = (∀p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (∃t. p = [t] ∧ action t ∈ α⇩f -B) ⟶ False)" by simp
  moreover have "... = (∀p s' t. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ p = [t] ∧ action t ∈ α⇩f -B ⟶ False)" by blast
  ultimately show "(∀p s'. validfinpath M s p s' ∧ (∃t. p = [t] ∧ action t ∈ α⇩f -B) ⟶ s' ∈ ⟦ff⟧ M e) = (∀a∈α⇩f -B. ∀s'. (s, a, s') ∉ transition M)" by auto
qed

theorem SHFAformula : 
  assumes "finite (-α⇩f) ∧ finite α⇩e ∧ finite (-B)"
  shows "s ∈ ⟦¬⇩μ⟨ρ ⋅ (Acts (-α⇩f)⇧⋆)⟩⇩R (⟨Acts α⇩e⟩⇩R tt ∨⇩μ (ν [Acts (-B)⇧⋆ ⋅ Acts (α⇩f -B)]⇩R ff ∧⇩μ (⋀⇩μa ∈ -B. ⟨Acts (-B)⇧⋆ ⋅ {a}⇩R⟩⇩R tt ⟹⇩R (μ var 1 ∧⇩μ (⟨a⟩⇩μ var 1 ∨⇩μ ⟨Acts (-α⇩f)⟩⇩R var 0)))))⟧ M e =
  (∄p. validpath M s p ∧ violating p ρ α⇩f α⇩e ∧ SHFA M B s p)"
  apply (rule Pformula[where ?Q="λa s. a ∈ reachableactions M B s" and ?A="λs p. relentlesslyreachable M B s p"]; (rule notoccursnotdepends)?; (simp only: assms(1) shiftdownDiamond shiftdownBox shiftdown.simps)?)
  unfolding SHFA_def
  apply simp+
  using notreachable_locked apply metis
  apply (simp add: relentlesslyreachable_def)
  apply simp
proof-
  have res1: "⋀a. ⟦Diamond (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Atom a)) tt⟧ M e = ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e" by simp
  moreover have res2: "⋀s a. s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Star (Acts (-B))) (diamond a tt)⟧ M e = (a ∈ reachableactions M B s)" using assms(1) Diamondreachable by metis
  ultimately show "⋀s a. a ∈ - B ⟹ (s ∈ ⟦Diamond (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Atom a)) tt⟧ M e) = (a ∈ reachableactions M B s)" by blast
  have "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦Box (Acts (α⇩f -B)) ff⟧ M e = (∀a∈α⇩f -B. s ∈ ⟦Box (Atom a) ff⟧ M e)" by (auto simp: assms(1))
  hence "⋀s. s ∈ ⟦Box (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Acts (α⇩f -B))) ff⟧ M e = (∀a∈α⇩f -B. s ∈ ⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (Box (Atom a) ff)⟧ M e)"
    apply (simp only: Box.simps(5))
    apply (simp only: Boxmatch matchstaract reachableactionsdef)
    using Boxmatch apply blast
    done
  hence "⋀s. (s ∈ ⟦Box (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Acts (α⇩f -B))) ff⟧ M e) = (∀a∈α⇩f -B. s ∈ ⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e)" by (simp only: Box.simps)
  moreover have "⋀s a. s ∈ ⟦Box (Star (Acts (-B))) (box a ff)⟧ M e = (a ∉ reachableactions M B s)" using Boxnotreachable assms(1) by metis
  ultimately show "⋀s. (s ∈ ⟦Box (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Acts (α⇩f -B))) ff⟧ M e) = (∀a∈α⇩f -B. s ∉ ⟦Diamond (Times (Star (Acts (-B))) (Atom a)) tt⟧ M e)" using res1 res2 by blast
qed
